nd mysticism in the\nrepresentation of the heavenly stairs, in order to show the cultural anchorage\nof the symbology employed in these cases [abridged].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jun 2015 22:49:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-29"}
